[6] Cholera, prisoners - India (Tamil Nadu)
Date: Tue, 24 Jan 2006
From: Charles Chambers <ayo6@cdc.gov>
Source: New Kerala.com [edited]
<http://www.newkerala.com/news.php?action=3Dfullnews&id=3D87789>

Tamil Nadu has 9 Central Prisons and the article [referred to] doesn't say
which one.
However, the source above, which includes the whole article, tells which
prison:
"It may be recalled that over 79 inmates of the Tiruchirapalli Central
Prison were taken ill with vomiting and diarrhea after they consumed the
food supplied in the prison."
--
Charles Chambers
LMIT/EDS, ATSDR
CDC, Atlanta GA
<ayo6@cdc.gov>
